      </Box>
    </ColorBox>
    <ColorBox>
      <Box HorizontalAlignment="Left" VerticalAlignment="Stretch" Margin="2">
        Attempted murder and battery are different; a fist fight is most likely assault. A shooting is most likely an
        attempt at murder.
