      <Box HorizontalAlignment="Left" VerticalAlignment="Stretch" Margin="2">
        To take part in a large group of personnel creating an unlawful public disturbance.
      </Box>
    </ColorBox>
    <ColorBox>
      <Box HorizontalAlignment="Left" VerticalAlignment="Stretch" Margin="2">
