      </Box>
    </ColorBox>
    <ColorBox>
      <Box HorizontalAlignment="Left" VerticalAlignment="Stretch" Margin="2">
        This only changes from attempted to full-on murder if the victim enters a state of being deceased, having to be resurrected.
      </Box>
